
Flow Overview:

1. Salesforce retrieves a colleague token via IDAnywhere and ForgeRock using the standard SAML + OBO pattern.
2. iCB receives the JWT token request from Salesforce.
3. iCB extracts the role attribute from the request token.
4. Token is exchanged using Egress Authn/Authz (see DECISION-3983 flow).
5. iCB stores token in local cache and sends access token to Florence.
6. Role information is shared with Florence Case Manager (outside the token).
